This is a brand page for the TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY trademark by Ensemble Capital Management, LLC 
                                in BURLINGAME, CA, 94010.
Write a review about a product or service associated with this TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY trademark.    
                                Or, contact the owner Ensemble Capital Management, LLC of the TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY trademark by filing a request to communicate with    
                                the Legal Correspondent for licensing, use, and/or questions related to the TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY trademark.
                           






On Monday, March 05, 2007,  a U.S. federal trademark registration was filed for 
                        TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY by 
                        Ensemble Capital Management, LLC, BURLINGAME, CA  94010.
                        The USPTO has given the TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY 
                        trademark serial  number of  77122427.  
                        The current federal status of this trademark filing is REGISTERED AND RENEWED.
                        The correspondent listed for TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY is 
                        
                        
                                            Cathy Stannard-Stockton of 
                                            Ensemble Capital Management, LLC,  SUITE 460, 1350 BAYSHORE BLVD Burlingame, CA 94010
                                .
                            The TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY trademark is filed in the category of 
                            
                                    Insurance & Financial Services
                                . 
                            The description provided to the USPTO for TACTICAL PHILANTHROPY 
                            is Providing online information in the field charitable monetary giving through financial and estate planning; Advice relating to investments; Investment advice; Investment consultation; Investment management. 
                            





