ENSEMBLE CAPITAL MANAGEMENT
IS AN INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT FIRM
WHOSE INTERESTS ALIGN WITH YOURS.















We offer CUSTOMIZED PORTFOLIO MANAGEMENT SERVICES,
FEE-ONLY OBJECTIVE ADVICE and UNPARALLELED CLIENT SERVICE.

Ensemble Capital Management builds focused investment portfolios to help you preserve your success and enhance your future.
Serving clients with assets ranging from about $2 million to over $95 million, Ensemble offers a high level of personalized service to individuals, families, trusts, foundations and nonprofits.









Investment Management

We believe that a LONG-TERM PERSPECTIVE is an investment advantage.


We believe that exceptional investment returns are based on superior original research and the willingness to think independently rather than follow the crowd. Our investment philosophy is rooted in the idea that stocks and bonds represent a claim on future cash flow and are not simply trading vehicles. Our deep fundamental research is designed to identify outstanding companies, whose future prospects are not fully appreciated by the market. We build focused portfolios of these investment opportunities with the intent to hold them for multi- year periods so that we can participate in what we believe will be their superior corporate performance.
We build personalized portfolios for each client, matching investments to a client’s goals, objectives and tolerance for volatility. Unlike many financial advisory firms that invest their clients’ assets in mutual funds or an in-house model portfolio, we invest in individual stocks and bonds that we deem most attractive for each client.We charge a simple investment management fee based on a percentage of your assets under our management. This investment management fee is the only fee we charge and we accept no commissions or other payments from third parties.
Learn more about our approach to INVESTMENT MANAGEMENT




